data.description:
This updated Ranch home boasts a central location within walking distance to shopping centers and local parks, only minutes from both CUSD 10 or parochial schools, and a short drive to STL or Scott Air Force Base. With 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, and a bonus room in the basement you will feel there is ample room to begin your new chapter. On the main floor, a pass-through office/nursery leads you to a large primary bedroom you will just have to see. Tucked away on its own end of the home, there is exit access to your custom paved patio with a cedar pergola for your morning coffee and peaceful moments. You will feel the nostalgia when walking in the basement theater room with stadium seating to create your own family memories! A large backyard with a half basketball court makes this home one you won't want to miss. Call your favorite realtor for a tour and a chance to hear "welcome home"!
See the full “Updates & Features Page” for more.
Occupancy Permit to be provided by Closing.
